1
00:04:20,660 --> 00:04:24,231
There's simply no way
to shield against
every weaponized agent.

2
00:04:24,363 --> 00:04:26,206
Instead, I can make
super-immune systems

3
00:04:26,266 --> 00:04:28,302
by strengthening
the human cellular response.

4
