But manipulating
the immune system is
dangerous and stupid.

6
00:04:33,939 --> 00:04:37,113
The President's
science advisors made it
absolutely clear,

7
00:04:37,709 --> 00:04:40,189
no human subjects.

8
00:04:56,663 --> 00:04:57,903
(SIZZLING)

9
