(COOING)

15
00:06:48,908 --> 00:06:50,216
What's it gonna be?

16
00:06:50,709 --> 00:06:53,451
Look at that, Bruce.
Want a dinosaur?

17
00:06:53,678 --> 00:06:54,816
Let's have a little fight.

18
00:06:54,880 --> 00:06:56,290
(DAVID ROARING)

19
00:06:56,348 --> 00:06:57,588
You don't scare me.

20
00:06:58,384 --> 00:06:59,658
(ROARING)

21
00:06:59,718 --> 00:07:01,288
That's a delicious eyeball.

22
00:07:01,387 --> 00:07:03,423
You're big and green
and scary. I'm gonna run away.

23
00:07:30,649 --> 00:07:33,062
Really, speaking of Cheryl,
guess what...

24
00:07:33,552 --> 00:07:35,122
Bruce, you're hurt!

25
00:07:36,389 --> 00:07:39,062
Jack hit him
with the stick, but Bruce
wouldn't hit him back.

26
00:07:39,125 --> 00:07:41,331
He just stood there, shaking.

27
00:07:41,927 --> 00:07:43,634
(WHISPERS) It's okay.

28
00:07:51,103 --> 00:07:52,808
Yeah, strange
he didn't make a peep.

29
00:07:52,872 --> 00:07:54,942
Any other kid would've
wailed his head off.

30
00:07:55,007 --> 00:07:59,387
That's Bruce. He's like that.
He's just so bottled up.

31
00:08:03,815 --> 00:08:06,887
The samples
we found in your lab,
they were human blood.

32
00:08:06,952 --> 00:08:08,829
You've ignored protocol.

33
00:08:09,689 --> 00:08:11,997
You had no right
snooping around in my lab.

34
00:08:12,290 --> 00:08:14,168
That's my business.
Wrong, Banner.

35
00:08:14,560 --> 00:08:17,302
It's government business,
and you're off the project.

36
00:08:35,681 --> 00:08:37,386
(ALARM BLARING)

37
00:08:39,784 --> 00:08:42,890
Attention, all personnel!
Fail-safe has been initiated.

38
00:08:42,955 --> 00:08:45,298
Gamma decontamination
will occur in 30 minutes.

39
00:08:45,357 --> 00:08:47,735
Evacuate immediately.
I repeat,

40
00:08:48,094 --> 00:08:49,971
evacuate immediately!

41
00:08:50,028 --> 00:08:51,599
(SIREN BLARING)

42
00:08:52,764 --> 00:08:53,971
(GASPS)

43
00:09:03,275 --> 00:09:04,583
(TIRES SCREECHING)

44
00:09:08,813 --> 00:09:11,259
Edith?
David, what's going on?

45
00:09:11,317 --> 00:09:14,456
I gotta talk to you, Edith.
EDITH: Bruce, stay here.

46
00:09:17,188 --> 00:09:18,530
What are you doing?

47
00:09:35,607 --> 00:09:36,915
(YELLING)

48
00:09:37,543 --> 00:09:38,817
(ROARING)

49
00:09:47,687 --> 00:09:50,190
(CONTINUES ROARING)

50
00:09:52,924 --> 00:09:54,335
EDITH: What are you doing?

51
00:09:54,427 --> 00:09:56,634
DAVID: I'm trying to tell you
what's gotta be done!

52
00:09:56,696 --> 00:09:59,732
David, please stop it! No!

53
00:09:59,798 --> 00:10:01,299
David, no!

54
00:10:02,201 --> 00:10:04,236
(EDITH SCREAMING)

55
00:10:05,671 --> 00:10:06,807
EDITH: No!
DAVID: Yes!

56
00:10:06,871 --> 00:10:08,908
David! No!

57
00:10:08,975 --> 00:10:11,182
(DAVID SCREAMING HYSTERICALLY)

58
00:10:13,745 --> 00:10:15,280
(BRUCE GROANING)

59
00:10:16,349 --> 00:10:17,691
Bruce.

60
00:10:17,984 --> 00:10:19,928
Bruce, wake up, Son.

61
00:10:20,519 --> 00:10:23,260
Bruce. Bruce.

62
00:10:27,058 --> 00:10:28,764
Another nightmare?

63
00:10:29,828 --> 00:10:31,239
I don't know.

64
00:10:31,831 --> 00:10:33,434
I don't remember.

65
00:10:35,768 --> 00:10:37,211
Hi, Mom.

66
00:10:39,205 --> 00:10:41,183
Already off to college.

67
00:10:42,107 --> 00:10:44,780
I'm gonna miss you terribly.
I'll miss you, too.

68
00:10:45,344 --> 00:10:47,619
Please, come here.

69
00:10:50,615 --> 00:10:54,586
Look at you. Soon to be
a great scientist.

70
00:10:55,354 --> 00:10:58,424
I guess. I mean, who knows?
I do.

71
00:10:59,457 --> 00:11:03,133
There's something
inside you so special.

72
00:11:04,663 --> 00:11:06,268
Some kind of greatness.

73
00:11:06,331 --> 00:11:10,438
I'm sure someday you're gonna
share it with the whole world.

74
00:12:06,225 --> 00:12:08,898
But as far as I'm concerned,
security ought to be...

75
00:12:08,961 --> 00:12:10,565
Good morning, Dr. Krenzler.
Good morning.

76
00:12:10,696 --> 00:12:12,697
Security ought to be
beefed up a lot more.

77
00:12:12,764 --> 00:12:14,971
In a place like this
you can't be too careful.

78
00:12:15,234 --> 00:12:18,613
Bruce! Big day.
Did you sleep?
I didn't sleep.

79
00:12:18,903 --> 00:12:21,782
