683
01:09:53,389 --> 01:09:55,765
He did?
It sounded bad, but...

684
01:09:57,626 --> 01:09:59,662
I honestly don't remember.

685
01:10:02,864 --> 01:10:04,867
The thing that worries me

686
01:10:05,466 --> 01:10:06,467
is

687
01:10:07,536 --> 01:10:11,448
