and probably right for you.

1044
01:47:01,046 --> 01:47:03,048
How far from the base
are you?

1045
01:47:03,115 --> 01:47:06,256
I'm already here.
They're taking
his father in now.

1046
01:47:06,886 --> 01:47:09,993
That's all good news.
Stay there, Betty.

1047
01:47:24,304 --> 01:47:27,216
PlLOT:
Legend One rolling in hot.
