OFFICER: Hold your fire
until my command!

1100
01:53:19,826 --> 01:53:22,328
MAN ON RADlO:
Engine 24 to command.
We are in position now.

1101
01:54:29,962 --> 01:54:31,463
You found me.

1102
01:54:33,966 --> 01:54:36,242
You weren't that hard to find.

1103
01:54:38,438 --> 01:54:39,847
Yes, I was.

1104
01:54:59,725 --> 01:55:01,170
(POLlCE RADlO CHATTERlNG)

1105
